<div style="text-align: right;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">rating:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+98</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="I like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="I don't like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="Cancel my vote" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
<p>Hey everyone. This is Zyn, wiki admin, captain of the site’s Forum Criticism Team, and co-author of 30+ pages on the site (written together with both new and experienced authors alike).</p>
<p>This page is here to tell you about co-authored pages, and offer some suggestions for all authors on how to go about writing them.</p>
<table style="margin:0; padding:0">
<tr>
<td style="margin:0; padding:0">
<div id="toc">
<div id="toc-action-bar"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.foldToc(event)">Fold</a><a style="display: none" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.unfoldToc(event)">Unfold</a></div>
<div class="title">Table of Contents</div>
<div id="toc-list">
<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc0">What is a co-authored page?</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc1">Why bother co-authoring?</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc2">I want to try co-authoring something! How do I find a co-author?</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc3">I think I found someone! What should I look for in a co-author?</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc4">But Zyn, what do I do if I haven’t written anything successful for the mainsite yet?</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc5">What is a collab sandbox?</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc6">Any last suggestions?</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</td>
